log-description-titleblacklist: Dispela samting bin lukim long ol hit lis bilong no larim nem.

titleblacklist:
# Dispela i stap lis bilong no larim nem. Nem na yusanem masis sampela tok long hia no save bin mekim.
# Yusim "#" long ol toktok.
# Dispela i stap wokim bilong narakain kes
titlewhitelist:
# Dispela i stap lis bilong larim nem. 
# Yusim "#" long ol toktok.
# Dispela i stap wokim bilong narakain kes
titleblacklist-forbidden-edit: Pes "$2" bin tambu na yu no larim mekim dispela pes. Em masim dispela tok long lis bilong no larim nem: $1
titleblacklist-forbidden-move: "$2" no save muvim long "$3", bikos nem "$3" i bin tambu na yu no larim mekim dispela pes. Em masim dispela tok long lis bilong no larim nem: $1
titleblacklist-forbidden-upload: Nem bilong fail "$2" i bin tambu na yu no larim mekim dispela fail. Em masim dispela tok long lis bilong no larim nem: $1
titleblacklist-forbidden-new-account: Yusanem "$2" i bin tambu na yu no larim mekim akaun igat dispela nem. Em masim dispela tok long lis bilong no larim nem: $1
titleblacklist-invalid:
Dispela {{PLURAL:$1|lain}} long lis bilong no larim nem {{PLURAL:$1|i stap}} no wokim gutpela;
plis fiksim {{PLURAL:$1|em}} bipo sevim:
titleblacklist-override: Go antap lis bilong no larim nem sapos em masis

Lukaut: Dispela pes i save tasol save senisim bilong ol admin na ol narapela yusa igat rait bilong tbgo antap bikos em masim dispela tok long list bilong no larim nem:
$1
